ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/talkingtech/2017/01/05/ford-plans-take-amazons-alexa-ride/96178556/|title=Ford plans to take Amazon's Alexa for a ride|last=Snider|first=Mike|date=5 January 2017|work=[[USA Today]]|access-date=9 January 2018}}</ref>\n* [[BMW]] vehicles (all 2018 models)<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/amazon-alexa-bmw-2018-2017-9?op=1|title=Amazon is adding Alexa to BMW cars in 2018|last=Muoio|first=Danielle|date=27 September 2017|work=[[Business Insider]]|access-date=9 January 2018}}</ref>\n* [[Mini (marque)|Mini]] vehicles (all 2018 models)<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.cars.com/articles/bmw-mini-assimilate-full-amazon-alexa-skill-set-1420697423670/|title=BMW, Mini Assimilate Full Amazon Alexa Skill Set|last=Normile|first=Brian|date=2 October 2017|work=[[Cars.com]]|access-date=9 January 2018}}</ref>\n* [[Toyota]] vehicles (select 2018 models)<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://fortune.com/2018/01/09/amazon-alexa-toyota-lexus/|title=Amazon's Alexa Is Coming to Some Toyota and Lexus Cars|last=Vanian|first=Johnathan|date=9 January 2018|work=[[Fortune (magazine)|Fortune]]|access-date=9 January 2018}}</ref>\n* [[Lexus]] vehicles (select 2018 models)<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2018/01/09/toyota-will-add-amazon-alexa-to-select-cars-in-2018.html|title=Toyota will add Amazon Alexa to select cars in 2018|last=Ferris|first=Robert|date=9 January 2018|work=[[CNBC]]|access-date=9 January 2018}}</ref>\n* [[Volkswagen]] vehicles (2018 models)<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.autocar.co.uk/car-news/new-cars/volkswagen-get-amazon-alexa-voice-control-connectivity-push|title=Volkswagen to get Amazon Alexa voice control in connectivity push|last=Beckwith|first=Jimi|date=28 September 2017|work=[[Autocar (magazine)|Autocar]]|access-date=3 May 2018}}</ref>\n* [[Garmin]] Speak<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://uncrate.com/article/garmin-speak/|title=Garmin Speak|last=|first=|date=|website=Uncrate|access-date=21 October 2017}}</ref>